<div class="page-header page-header--centered">
  <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
</div>

<div class="page-container--narrow">
  <div class="split-layout" data-testid="about-layout">
    <div class="split-layout__media">
      <%= image_tag "about.jpg",
            class: "split-layout__media-image",
            alt: "Niklas Bergstrom",
            data: { testid: "about-photo" } %>
    </div>

    <div class="split-layout__cards">
      <div class="show-panel about-card" data-testid="about-bio-1">
        <p class="about-card__eyebrow">
          <%= lucide_icon "briefcase", size: 14 %>
          Professional
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm a Test Manager and IT Consultant based in Brisbane,
          Australia, with over 25 years of experience across
          government, financial services, utilities, healthcare, and
          telecommunications.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="show-panel about-card" data-testid="about-bio-2">
        <p class="about-card__eyebrow">
          <%= lucide_icon "mountain", size: 14 %>
          Outdoors
        </p>
        <p>
          Love the outdoors and spend a lot of time rock climbing,
          canyoning, and biking. Our camper van is frequently used and
          I'm always looking for the next adventure.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="show-panel about-card" data-testid="about-bio-3">
        <p class="about-card__eyebrow">
          <%= lucide_icon "code-2", size: 14 %>
          Building in public
        </p>
        <p>
          bergstromdomain.com is where I build things in public. It
          started as a way to get properly hands-on with Rails again,
          and it's become a place to work through Claude and Claude
          Code as part of the day-to-day toolkit too — the blog series
          documents the actual process, bugs included.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
